title: FSX - Perfect Flight - Ultimate CRJ-700
description:
Final CRJ-700 simulation is a complete set "yn-one" add-on for Microsoft Flight Simulator X that offers a complete representation of Bombarfier CRJ-700 in 12 different textures: American Eagle, Continental Airlines, Delta Connection, CR Airways, Alaska Airlines, JAZZ, Conviasa, HOP, SA Express, Star Alliance, British Airways, United Express. 
Product also includes a set of realistic collection of multi-crew airline missions to replicate the actual flight operations.
